import React, {useState} from 'react' import stickersData from './AuctionStikers-data' function Sticker(props){ const index = props.index const onClick = props.onClick const stickersDataIndex = stickersData[index] const time = stickersDataIndex.time.split(':'); return(
{stickersDataIndex.profile.nickname}
{stickersDataIndex.stickname}
{time[0]} час
{time[1]} мин
{time[2]} сек
) } export default Sticker
